Achievements track long-term progress across combat, exploration,
social activity, economy, quests, and guild-specific milestones.

Each achievement line has named tiers:

  Bronze
  Silver
  Gold
  Platinum
  Mythic

Use these commands:

  achievements          view your achievement journal
  achievements titles   list your unlocked achievement titles
  atitle                equip or clear an achievement title
  leaderboard           view the top 50 achievement rankings

Achievement progress is driven by tracked game stats. Most progress is
permanent once earned. New unlocks can grant titles that you may equip
separately from your normal title.

See also: help achievements, help achievement_titles, help leaderboard
